    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（さっきからずっと、渚は新しいレシピの）\n（ジュースを考えているが……）",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cooking-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "出来ました！　{user}さん！\nズバリ、桃そのままジュースです！",
      "startTime": 8.343219916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "桃にストローを刺しただけでは……？\n凄く野性的な見た目になっているぞ……",
      "startTime": 14.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "果汁と果肉をそのまま楽しめる\n画期的なメニューです！",
      "startTime": 19.9695235252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに画期的だが、ジュースと言われると\n違うような気がするな……",
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか……ココナッツのジュースみたいで\nいいかなと思ったんですが……",
      "startTime": 30.8341716766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ次はこっちです。桃と練乳と砂糖を\n一緒にミキサーで混ぜてみました",
      "startTime": 37.5341716766,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2832.4949900999954,
          "startTime": 40.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……うっ！　もの凄く甘い……砂糖の入れ過ぎで\nなんだかジャリジャリするぞ……",
      "startTime": 46.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに砂糖を入れ過ぎじゃないか？\nもう少し甘さ控えめの方が……",
      "startTime": 51.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "甘さを抑える、ですか……\nそれなら、こっちはどうでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 57.974323686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "凍らせた桃をミキサーにかけてシャーベット状に\nしてみました！　冷たくて美味しいですよ！",
      "startTime": 63.7076570194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……次はどんなとんでもないジュースが……\nおお、これは美味しいぞ。甘さもちょうどいい",
      "startTime": 72.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "はちみつを入れることで優しい甘さを出しつつ\n桃の風味を損なわないように調整してみたんです",
      "startTime": 80.5625100137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "今日作ったメニューの中では一番の自信作です！\nどうですか？",
      "startTime": 87.9958504678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、凄くいいメニューだと思うぞ\n桃の素材の味が活きている気がする",
      "startTime": 92.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　やったぁ……！",
      "startTime": 95.0728017331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、このジュースをもう少しだけ改良して\nオリジナルメニューとして提出したいです！",
      "startTime": 101.7031749409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "商品名は、そうですね……\n『桃、凍らせてみた！』……とかで！",
      "startTime": 108.6698410989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（次はまともな商品名を考えるのに）\n（時間がかかりそうだな……）",
      "startTime": 114.7000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 117.436149947,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1500,
          "startTime": 118.936149947
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、見て下さい{user}さん！\nあそこに美味しそうなケーキ屋さんがありますよ！",
      "startTime": 122.5361504556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "新作のイチゴづくしケーキかぁ\n期間限定らしいですよ。美味しそう……",
      "startTime": 129.1694832803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あっちにあるのはチーズドッグですよね\n同じクラスの子が美味しかったって言ってました！",
      "startTime": 136.8028166136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "渚。今日の目的を忘れてないか……？",
      "startTime": 140.3640568896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "も、もちろんです！　忘れてなんかないですよ\n今日はキッチンカーを見に来たんです",
      "startTime": 147.8050613087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "一日店長をする前に、一度下見をしたいって\nお願いしたのは私ですから",
      "startTime": 153.6050531706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そう言いながらも視線はケーキ屋さんに\n向いているように見えるんだが",
      "startTime": 158.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "き、気のせいですよ！\nあ、キッチンカーってあれじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 163.0763682684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "わ～結構大きいんですね。外装も可愛いです\nジュースの種類も沢山あるみたいですね",
      "startTime": 174.2763753892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "今はお客さんもあまり並んでないし\n何か買って飲んでみるか？",
      "startTime": 180.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……梨のフローズンジュースを飲んでみても\nいいですか？　私が作ったメニューに似てますし",
      "startTime": 186.4793687185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。買って来るから待っていてくれ",
      "startTime": 190.4710762187,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5308.261648500007,
          "startTime": 195.7793378672
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
